{"tid":1547360,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"首先，我們需要對這次革命存有信仰","createTime":"2019-09-06T15:51:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T01:56:36.000Z","uid":277913,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"61372d4267c7e6b8cd2acc345cd328218c9615c1","tid":1547360,"uid":277913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:51:41.000Z","msg":"今日淩晨，又有阿伯出嚟斬人之後揚長而去<br />\n計計埋埋，呢種阿伯斬人事件都已經有六七單<br />\n咁問題就嚟喇，點解阿伯夠膽落街斬人?<br />\n因為佢相信，佢身後既政府同黨係永遠都唔會崩潰，正如老大哥會永遠統治第一空降場一樣<br />\n所以佢夠膽去斬人，佢有自信無人可以秋後算帳<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">重點係信仰</span></strong></span><br />\n其實無人能夠證明共匪可以千秋萬世，但係佢信<br />\n大陸宜家要攞配給券買豬肉，但係佢信<br />\n共匪黃俄係永生不滅，直到永遠<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">咁你又信唔信呢?</span></strong></span><br />\n好多人話香港注定輸，邊個知啊<br />\n你信佢會輸，佢咪真係輸囉<br />\n你信佢會贏，你咪玩激啲囉<br />\n你可以訪問吓阿伯，如果天日革命成功咗，你咁做我哋會攞你去淩遲過喎<br />\n佢會話你聽，屌你都0N99既，共產黨係永生不滅架<br />\n<br />\n你信革命會成功，你咪玩激啲囉<br />\n你信革命會成功，你咪學阿伯咁囉<br />\n無話一定乜乜乜，但係你如果連比信仰都輸<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">咁你就抵撚死啦ON99</span>"},{"pid":"70c3c1f99ff0cc7f8834e7d80498754f59692d23","tid":1547360,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:55:25.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1545337/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1545337/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cd960aa6eb578012e997739bfbeeff4db579a2e2","tid":1547360,"uid":277913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:58:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"59aa3296555ebe7cee845be15e4f7e91f60aa52f","tid":1547360,"uid":17719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T16:15:55.000Z","msg":"我完全同意 見到d人俾共產黨威嚇嘅手段 而唔支持其他人追求嘅野真係覺得好弱"},{"pid":"9e6f0fa3170104693ac7e06e6f549e686f5c518b","tid":1547360,"uid":277913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T16:37:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7f0d91b33c1da2aa42819d75c0001611ef0cca9a","tid":1547360,"uid":277913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T01:56:36.000Z","msg":"推"}]}